) a further\ntemplate family, which would produce essentially exact waveforms written\ndirectly in terms of the physical spin parameters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 Nov 2002 18:19:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 16 Apr 2003 22:28:07 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 24 Mar 2005 19:53:26 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 26 Jul 2006 15:30:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-11-17"}
